Magma Power Co said director ArnoldL. Johnson has been named president and chief executiveofficer.    He succeeds Andrew W. Hoch, who moved to chairman inFebruary following the resignation of B.C. McCabe Sr.    The company said Johnson has also been named president andchief executive officer of Magma Energy Inc &lt;MAGE>, which MagmaPower controls, succeeding Hoch, who becomes Magma Energychairman as well. McCabe, whom Hoch also succeeds there, hasbeen named chairman emeritus. Reuter&#3;